OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FSome cloud will feed
OL,6,Fsouthwards across the region on
OL,7,FTuesday, bringing a small risk of a
OL,8,Fshower. However, most places staying
OL,9,Fdry and still feeling hot where the
OL,10,Fsun appears.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FThe
OL,13,Fweather will stay warm through the
OL,14,Fweek, though cooler than recently.
OL,15,FThere will be some sunshine at times,
OL,16,Fthough a chance of a few showers,
OL,17,Fwhich could turn thundery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
